Using money raised in offerings, the cult has built an orbital fortress around this planet.
There aren't many acolytes here yet, but the defense systems are already tight and strong.
We will provide you a stealth starfighter that can penetrate the force shields and get you to the docking station.
After that, it will be up to you to mount an individual siege against the fortress's defenses.
Somewhere inside, there is a map with Yellow Father's location. If you manage to break in, we will be able to retrieve it.
